      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079984218112
    m_Localized: "Le travail d'\xE9quipe, c'est le r\xEAve de l'\xE9quipe, pas vrai
      ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080084881408
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080185544704
    m_Localized: Je suis tellement plein.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080286208000
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080386871296
    m_Localized: '*sluurrrp* *miam* *pouf*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080487534592
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080592392192
    m_Localized: Ignorer la racine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080693055488
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080789524480
    m_Localized: "BONJOUR ! Bienvenue \xE0 la PortaBank (MC) ! Votre solution bancaire
      portable num\xE9ro un !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080894382080
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080990851072
    m_Localized: Faites-moi signe si vous avez des questions !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081095708672
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081196371968
    m_Localized: "J'ai eu ces super remises sur des hangars portables remis \xE0
      neuf ! Tu y crois ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081297035264
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081401892864
    m_Localized: "Oh, l'odeur ? C'\xE9tait comme \xE7a quand on a achet\xE9 la flotte."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081502556160
    m_Localized: "Pr\xE9pos\xE9 Porta"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081603219456
    m_Localized: "J'ai eu ce petit sapin d\xE9sodorisant pour aider \xE0 rafra\xEEchir
      l'air !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081703882752
    m_Localized: Chef des Moines
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081804546048
    m_Localized: "Non non non, \xE7a ne va pas. T'as beaucoup trop de cheveux !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081905209344
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082005872640
    m_Localized: Erk.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082106535936
    m_Localized: Chef des Moines
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082207199232
    m_Localized: ALORS POURQUOI ES-TU ICI ?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082312056832
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082412720128
    m_Localized: "N\u0153ud racine \xE0 ignorer"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082513383424
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082614046720
    m_Localized: "*Bisou* Je suis tellement contente de te voir. Tu dois avoir eu
      une longue journ\xE9e."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082714710016
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082819567616
    m_Localized: Pourquoi tu manges pas un petit quelque chose et tu vas te coucher
      ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082920230912
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083020894208
    m_Localized: Bonjour, dormeur ! Tu vas aller en ville aujourd'hui ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083121557504
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083222220800
    m_Localized: "Je pense \xE0 me prendre un de ces petits robots pour nettoyer
      la maison."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083327078400
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083427741696
    m_Localized: "Comment \xE7a s'appelle encore ? Vwoomba ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083532599296
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083641651200
    m_Localized: "J'ai entendu qu'un nouveau caf\xE9 mignon a ouvert en ville. On
      devrait y aller un de ces jours !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083746508800
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083851366400
    m_Localized: Fais attention aux animaux sauvages. Ils s'approchent de plus en
      plus des sentiers ces derniers temps. Effrayant !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083956224000
    m_Localized: "Fille Branch\xE9e"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084061081600
    m_Localized: "On dirait que je me suis encore enferm\xE9e dehors"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084170133504
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084274991104
    m_Localized: Mmm-hmm ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084375654400
    m_Localized: "Fille Branch\xE9e"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084480512000
    m_Localized: Ouais, je veux dire, je te jure que c'est chez moi
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084589563904
    m_Localized: "Fille Branch\xE9e"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084719587328
    m_Localized: "En quoi \xE7a te regarde de toute fa\xE7on ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084837027840
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084967051264
    m_Localized: "N\u0153ud Racine"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085084491776
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085206126592
    m_Localized: Un mille, deux mille, trois mille
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085323567104
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085436813312
    m_Localized: . . . quatre mille, cinq mille, six mille
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085566836736
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085684277248
    m_Localized: . . . sept mille, huit mille, neuf mille
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085801717760
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085923352576
    m_Localized: . . . dix mille, onze mille, douze mille
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086040793088
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086158233600
    m_Localized: ". . . dix-sept mille . . . attends, j'en \xE9tais o\xF9 ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086275674112
    m_Localized: Le Compteur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086393114624
    m_Localized: "Mince, tu m'as fait me tromper, il faut que je recommence depuis
      le d\xE9but !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086502166528
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086607024128
    m_Localized: "T'es enfin arriv\xE9. Je m'appelle Phil, et je viens avec un message
      urgent."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086716076032
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086837710848
    m_Localized: T'es une tasse de nouilles qui parle ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086959345664
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087080980480
    m_Localized: "J'ai peut-\xEAtre l'air d'une d\xE9licieuse tasse de nouilles,
      mais je suis en r\xE9alit\xE9 une intelligence artificielle sophistiqu\xE9e."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087198420992
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087315861504
    m_Localized: Attends . . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087424913408
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087533965312
    m_Localized: "C'\xE9tait quoi \xE7a ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087643017216
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087760457728
    m_Localized: . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087869509632
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087974367232
    m_Localized: "Ils doivent avancer plus vite que je pensais. On doit trouver des
      baguettes imm\xE9diatement."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088087613440
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088196665344
    m_Localized: "Une fois que t'as les baguettes, tu dois verser de l'eau chaude
      sur moi et m\xE9langer mes nouilles."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088314105856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088423157760
    m_Localized: . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088528015360
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088632872960
    m_Localized: Euh ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088737730560
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088842588160
    m_Localized: Ok ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088947445760
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089052303360
    m_Localized: "D\xE9sol\xE9, c'est pas le moment d'expliquer. Vite !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089152966656
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089257824256
    m_Localized: "Texte par d\xE9faut \xE0 remplacer"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089362681856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089463345152
    m_Localized: "Il reste une derni\xE8re \xE9tape pour l'incantation. Tu dois trouver
      une sauce piquante extr\xEAmement \xE9pic\xE9e."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089568202752
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089668866048
    m_Localized: T'as la sauce piquante -- vite, verse-la dans moi.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089773723648
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089878581248
    m_Localized: Euhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089983438848
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090088296448
    m_Localized: "Beurk, non, pas comme \xE7a. Fais-le juste."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090188959744
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090289623040
    m_Localized: Je crois qu'ils en ont en stock dans les distributeurs automatiques.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090398674944
    m_Localized: Bronzeur
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090507726848
    m_Localized: Tu peux bouger ? Tu bloques mon soleil
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090612584448
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090713247744
    m_Localized: Oui
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090818105344
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090922962944
    m_Localized: Non
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091027820544
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091128483840
    m_Localized: "Hein ? Non, j'ai pas besoin d'\xEAtre sauv\xE9e."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091233341440
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091334004736
    m_Localized: "J'essayais juste de montrer \xE0 ces nerds comment faire leur travail."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091438862336
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091543719936
    m_Localized: "Bref, on s'en va d'ici Frankie, on a du travail \xE0 faire avec
      Maya en haut."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091644383232
    m_Localized: "Travailleur Qualifi\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091749240832
    m_Localized: Racine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091849904128
    m_Localized: "Travailleur Qualifi\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091954761728
    m_Localized: "H\xE9, euh, si tu veux descendre ces escaliers vers la salle \xE9lectrique,
      tu vas devoir m'affronter en lutte."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092059619328
    m_Localized: "Travailleur Qualifi\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092164476928
    m_Localized: "Tu veux te mesurer \xE0 moi ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092265140224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092365803520
    m_Localized: Absolument !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092470661120
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092575518720
    m_Localized: Merci, euh, je vais passer pour l'instant.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092680376320
    m_Localized: "Travailleur Qualifi\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092781039616
    m_Localized: "Ah, mon dos ! T'as compl\xE8tement f***\xE9 mon dos !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092881702912
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092986560512
    m_Localized: "Texte par d\xE9faut \xE0 remplacer"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093091418112
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093196275712
    m_Localized: "*couic* Je suis tellement stress\xE9 *couic* ces d\xE9lais sont
      insens\xE9s."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093301133312
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093405990912
    m_Localized: '*couic* Oh, je suis tellement content de te voir.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093510848512
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093615706112
    m_Localized: "On dirait que tout est revenu \xE0 la normale."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093716369408
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093821227008
    m_Localized: Et mon fonds de retraite coule . . . *couic triste*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093921890304
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094026747904
    m_Localized: "Comment je vais subvenir aux besoins de ma famille comme \xE7a
      ? *couic d\xE9sesp\xE9r\xE9*"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094127411200
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094232268800
    m_Localized: Hmm
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094337126400
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094437789696
    m_Localized: Euhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094542647296
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094647504896
    m_Localized: "*couic* Je suis d'accord, Frankie. On doit renverser nos ma\xEEtres
      capitalistes."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094748168192
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094848831488
    m_Localized: Erk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094953689088
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095058546688
    m_Localized: Euhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095163404288
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095268261888
    m_Localized: "Merci de m'avoir donn\xE9 ce super conseil. *couic heureux* T'es
      vraiment un bon ami."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095373119488
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095473782784
    m_Localized: "L'\xE9lectricit\xE9 a vacill\xE9, et ensuite les stagiaires sont
      devenus fous."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095578640384
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095683497984
    m_Localized: "S'il y en a un qui peut r\xE9gler \xE7a, c'est toi. Fais attention
      ! *couic inspirant*"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095788355584
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095893213184
    m_Localized: "C'est comme si personne n'avait m\xEAme remarqu\xE9 que le courant
      \xE9tait coup\xE9. Bizarre."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096006459392
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096115511296
    m_Localized: '*couic effrayant*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096220368896
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096329420800
    m_Localized: Racine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096463638528
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096568496128
    m_Localized: "Hol\xE0 hol\xE0 hol\xE0, ne me fais pas de mal !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096673353728
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096774017024
    m_Localized: "Je suis peut-\xEAtre chauve, mais je suis pas un de ces FOUS."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096878874624
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096983732224
    m_Localized: "H\xE9, \xE9coute, si t'as besoin d'un moyen de sortir d'ici, je
      peux te ramener \xE0 la PortaBank juste en dehors de l'\xE9glise."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097088589824
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097193447424
    m_Localized: Bref, tu veux sauvegarder ta progression jusqu'ici ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097298305024
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097403162624
    m_Localized: Oui, allons-y !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097508020224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097617072128
    m_Localized: Non, merci.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097721929728
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097826787328
    m_Localized: "Tu veux que je te ram\xE8ne \xE0 la PortaBank ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097927450624
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098036502528
    m_Localized: Non, merci.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098137165824
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098242023424
    m_Localized: Oui, sors-moi d'ici !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098346881024
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098455932928
    m_Localized: Le lit douillet t'appelle . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098556596224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098665648128
    m_Localized: Bonjour, lit douillet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098770505728
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098875363328
    m_Localized: "T'es s\xFBr de vouloir aller dormir ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098980220928
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099085078528
    m_Localized: Ouais
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099189936128
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099294793728
    m_Localized: "Non, j'ai du travail \xE0 faire"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099399651328
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099504508928
    m_Localized: "\xC0 la prochaine."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099609366528
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099714224128
    m_Localized: Vraiment ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099819081728
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099923939328
    m_Localized: En y repensant . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100028796928
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100137848832
    m_Localized: "Ouais, j'en suis s\xFBr."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100246900736
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100351758336
    m_Localized: "Tu peux pas revenir en arri\xE8re, tu sais ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100456615936
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100561473536
    m_Localized: Je sais.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100666331136
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100775383040
    m_Localized: Attends, je le pensais pas !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100880240640
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100985098240
    m_Localized: "Ok. \xC0 plus."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101089955840
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101199007744
    m_Localized: Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101303865344
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101412917248
    m_Localized: "Tu peux m'aider avec ce probl\xE8me ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101517774848
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101622632448
    m_Localized: Ok
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101727490048
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101836541952
    m_Localized: Non
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101941399552
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102046257152
    m_Localized: "Tu devrais pas trop me g\xE2ter, je n'aurai jamais une vraie \xE9thique
      de travail si tu continues comme \xE7a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102151114752
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102255972352
    m_Localized: "T'as raison. Je dois vraiment m'en occuper moi-m\xEAme."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102365024256
    m_Localized: "Moine Captiv\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102469881856
    m_Localized: "J'ai embrass\xE9 mon destin. Chauve c'est le pouvoir !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102578933760
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102683791360
    m_Localized: Salut ! Je suis pas ton ennemi, juste un campagnol qui veut te donner
      quelques conseils !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102788648960
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102893506560
    m_Localized: "Dans cette d\xE9mo tu affronteras des ennemis de difficult\xE9
      vari\xE9e pour \xE9valuer tes aptitudes au combat"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102998364160
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103103221760
    m_Localized: Ouais ouais.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103208079360
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103312936960
    m_Localized: Oui, eh bien, sois averti ! Le combat ne se met pas en pause dans
      Frankie ! Une fois qu'un ennemi peut attaquer, il le fera !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103417794560
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103526846464
    m_Localized: "Pour vaincre ton ennemi, s\xE9lectionne rapidement une comp\xE9tence
      avec les touches directionnelles HAUT-BAS-GAUCHE-DROITE ou W-A-S-D, et confirme
      avec \xAB E \xBB. Ensuite s\xE9lectionne simplement ta cible et appuie \xE0
      nouveau sur \xAB E \xBB !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103627509760
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103736561664
    m_Localized: "\xC0 mesure que tu acquiers de nouvelles comp\xE9tences, tu devras
      naviguer plus profond\xE9ment dans ton arbre de comp\xE9tences avec les m\xEAmes
      touches directionnelles. On traversera ce pont quand on y arrivera !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103841419264
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103946276864
    m_Localized: Mmm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104051134464
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104155992064
    m_Localized: "OK ! C'est tout. C'est tout, tu veux que je r\xE9p\xE8te ces instructions
      ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104265043968
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104365707264
    m_Localized: Non
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104474759168
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104579616768
    m_Localized: Oui
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104692862976
    m_Localized: Belle Tapisserie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104801914880
    m_Localized: Bonjour Francis
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104915161088
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105061961728
    m_Localized: Tu me parles ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105175207936
    m_Localized: Belle Tapisserie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105280065536
    m_Localized: "\xC0 qui d'autre ?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105389117440
    m_Localized: Belle Tapisserie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105498169344
    m_Localized: Tu veux me rejoindre, Francis ??
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105615609856
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105728856064
    m_Localized: Oui
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105837907968
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105946959872
    m_Localized: "Bien s\xFBr"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106056011776
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106165063680
    m_Localized: Euhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106274115584
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106383167488
    m_Localized: Oui
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106496413696
    m_Localized: Belle Tapisserie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106605465600
    m_Localized: Chauve c'est beau.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106714517504
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106823569408
    m_Localized: Chauve
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106932621312
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107041673216
    m_Localized: Chauve c'est
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107150725120
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107259777024
    m_Localized: Chauve c'est beau.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107368828928
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107477880832
    m_Localized: Attends ! Je suis pas encore parti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107586932736
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107695984640
    m_Localized: Je dois savoir . . . t'es team edward ou team jacob ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107800842240
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107909894144
    m_Localized: Oh. Oh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108018946048
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108127997952
    m_Localized: "Peu importe, \xE7a arrive. L'au-del\xE0."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108237049856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108341907456
    m_Localized: Bonne chance, Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108450959360
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108560011264
    m_Localized: "H\xE9, si jamais tu trouves un nouvel \xE9l\xE9ment pour ta tenue
      . . ."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108669063168
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108778115072
    m_Localized: Tu sais, comme un clavier ? Ou un gilet ? Ou une montre ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108887166976
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108996218880
    m_Localized: "Assure-toi de l'\xE9quiper dans le menu Tenue ! \xC7a sert \xE0
      rien que \xE7a reste dans ton sac \xE0 dos sans \xEAtre \xE9quip\xE9 !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109105270784
    m_Localized: "D\xE9faut"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109214322688
    m_Localized: Euh ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109323374592
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109432426496
    m_Localized: "Oh, t'es vraiment frais, toi. Acc\xE8de aux menus du joueur en
      appuyant sur la touche `TAB`."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109537284096
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109646336000
    m_Localized: Rebonjour, Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109755387904
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109864439808
    m_Localized: Bonjour, lit douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109973491712
    m_Localized: Lit Douillet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110082543616
    m_Localized: On y va ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110191595520
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110300647424
    m_Localized: "Oui s'il te pla\xEEt"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110409699328
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110518751232
    m_Localized: "N\u0153ud racine ignor\xE9"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110627803136
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110736855040
    m_Localized: Bats-moi et je te dirai un secret. *hue hue hue hue hue hue hue*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110845906944
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110954958848
    m_Localized: "Hngh. T'as vraiment eu ma peau. Bon, voil\xE0 mon secret."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111064010752
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111173062656
    m_Localized: "Apr\xE8s avoir un peu aventur\xE9, v\xE9rifie ton compte en banque.
      Tu pourrais \xEAtre surpris de voir que tes actions ont vers\xE9 quelques dividendes."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111277920256
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111391166464
    m_Localized: "Il y a une PortaBank (MC) juste \xE0 l'ext\xE9rieur de ce b\xE2timent
      de bureaux."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111500218368
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111609270272
    m_Localized: La question est, tu crois que tu peux me battre ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111718322176
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111827374080
    m_Localized: Non.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111936425984
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112045477888
    m_Localized: Oui ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112158724096
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112267776000
    m_Localized: Nah.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112376827904
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112485879808
    m_Localized: Absolument pas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112590737408
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112699789312
    m_Localized: "\xC9LOIGNE-TOI.DE.MON.MICRO-ONDES.FRANKIE."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112808841216
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112917893120
    m_Localized: Ouais ouais, ok, ouais ouais
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113026945024
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113135996928
    m_Localized: Ouais, ouais, non ouais, euh, ouais, non ouais
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113240854528
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113354100736
    m_Localized: Excusez-moi, vous pouvez patienter une seconde ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113463152640
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113572204544
    m_Localized: "Un gamin \xE9coute ma conversation"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113681256448
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113790308352
    m_Localized: "H\xE9 toi -- ouais, toi -- occupe-toi de tes affaires !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113903554560
    m_Localized: Gars des Nouvelles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114012606464
    m_Localized: "Ok, j'en \xE9tais o\xF9 ? Ouais ouais, euhh non ouais, ouais ouais."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114125852672
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114234904576
    m_Localized: "C'est moi, ton campagnol serviable du voisinage pr\xE9f\xE9r\xE9
      !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114343956480
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114453008384
    m_Localized: Voici un autre conseil ! Tu peux changer l'ordre du groupe et ajouter
      ou retirer des membres en utilisant les toilettes au bureau !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114562060288
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114671112192
    m_Localized: "Bien s\xFBr, tu dois avoir plus que juste TOI dans le groupe, Frankie
      !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114780164096
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114893410304
    m_Localized: C'est tout pour l'instant !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115002462208
    m_Localized: Campagnol Serviable
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115111514112
    m_Localized: Couic !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115224760320
    m_Localized: "D\xE9faut"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115338006528
    m_Localized: "Texte par d\xE9faut \xE0 remplacer"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115451252736
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115560304640
    m_Localized: On est vraiment fiers de ce que t'as accompli ici. T'es vraiment
      un Travailleur A++.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115673550848
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115782602752
    m_Localized: "On a h\xE2te de voir ce que tu feras ensuite. Continue comme \xE7a
      !"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115891654656
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116000706560
    m_Localized: "Maintenant que je t'ai suffisamment compliment\xE9, j'ai besoin
      que tu me rendes un service. Maya a des *DOCUMENTS TR\xC8S IMPORTANTS*."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116109758464
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116218810368
    m_Localized: "Merci d'avoir livr\xE9 ces *DOCUMENTS TR\xC8S IMPORTANTS*."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116327862272
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116436914176
    m_Localized: "Je dois maintenant examiner plus attentivement ces *DOCUMENTS TR\xC8S
      IMPORTANTS*."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116545966080
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116659212288
    m_Localized: "Tu peux prendre ta pause de 15 minutes -- j'ai activ\xE9 l'acc\xE8s
      \xE0 l'ascenseur pour la cuisine."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116768264192
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116877316096
    m_Localized: Descends ce toboggan de pompier -- oui, celui qui dit DANGER --
      et trouve les documents.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116990562304
    m_Localized: Cheval
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117099614208
    m_Localized: Du nouveau ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117208666112
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117321912320
    m_Localized: Frankie Frankie Frankie Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117430964224
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117540016128
    m_Localized: Je m'appelle Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117649068032
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117758119936
    m_Localized: C'est un peu comme Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117871366144
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117980418048
    m_Localized: Suis-je toi ? Es-tu moi ?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118089469952
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118198521856
    m_Localized: Ignorer la racine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118307573760
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118416625664
    m_Localized: Oh non oh non oh non oh non.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118525677568
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118634729472
    m_Localized: "Frankie ! J'ai besoin de ton aide, j'ai vraiment merd\xE9 cette
      fois."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118743781376
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118852833280
    m_Localized: "J'ai d\xE9fi\xE9 Tilly de descendre le toboggan de pompier dans
      la salle \xE0 balles et ELLE L'A FAIT. Maintenant elle est coinc\xE9e avec
      les stagiaires."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118961885184
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119075131392
    m_Localized: "\xC9coute, Cheval a verrouill\xE9 la porte de la salle \xE0 balles,
      mais tu peux rejoindre Tilly au sous-sol avec l'ascenseur."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119184183296
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119293235200
    m_Localized: "Allez Frankie, s'il te pla\xEEt va trouver Tilly. Elle va me tuer
      si on la laisse l\xE0-dedans."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119406481408
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119515533312
    m_Localized: Oh, euh, salut Tilly. Content de, euh . . . te revoir . . . de bonne
      humeur.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119624585216
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119737831424
    m_Localized: "Merci Frankie, je te dois vraiment une fi\xE8re chandelle."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119846883328
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119955935232
    m_Localized: "Fais attention aux stagiaires, ils sont vraiment remont\xE9s \xE0
      cause de quelque chose."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
